ity of artificial roosts for bats and decrease risks to occupants. Because continued loss of natural roosts may increase reliance on alternatives, such as artificial roosts, it is imperative that this conservation practice be improved.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Crawford, Reed D.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "O'Keefe, Joy M.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/b5378c6a352660433817dceab5d6b5d9", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/de002e5775b761a4b6afe394a755310676d83b9ee82937d99a9184898d7bba8f", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/GHYMXI4I", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/GHYMXI4I", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/6b15349eaf6e00b225ecb4dd41c05f67!/b18216-20795", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "1", "pages": "e14170", "title": "Conservation Biology", "volume": "38"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/b5378c6a352660433817dceab5d6b5d9"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:GHYMXI4I"}, {"identifier": "10.1111/cobi.14170"}], "communities": [{"id": "biosyslit"}, {"id": "batlit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_